<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<title>MinecraftLTI</title>
<style>
body {
	padding: 0 1em;
}
h1 {
	background: url("/dirt.png") repeat-x;
	padding: 8px;
	height: 24px;
	font-size: 24px;
	padding: 12px;
	color: #fff;
	font-weight: normal;
	border-radius: 5px;
}
ul {
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}
li {
	list-style: none;
	background-color: #ded;
	margin: 1em 0;
	padding: 0.25em 1em;
	border-radius: 5px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>MinecraftLTI</h1>
<form method="POST" action="/assignment">
<ul>
	<li>
		<p>To join, add this address to your multiplayer servers list:</p>
		<pre>${address}</pre>
	</li>
	<li>
		<p>To add this tool to your LMS, visit <a href="/config.xml">/config.xml</a> for the configuration values and <a href="/consumer">/consumer</a> to generate a key and secret.</p>
	</li>
</ul>
</form>
</body>
</html>
